[{"Id": 1016779, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "In \"Tuhfatu Ridawiyah\" he said: Allamah Taqi, Sayyid Mirza Hasan bin Sayyid Mirza Ali Agha Shirazi (may Allah glorifies his secret) told me of the following supplication, he mentioned that it was from the proof (may Allah hasten his relief) and some pious scholars has also narrated it. He (may Allah have mercy on him) said: you recite it after everyday compulsory prayers and at any other time, it suffices you in your important requests and makes you reach your goal…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Tohfatul Razaviya mein Marhoom Allama Sayed Hasan bin Marhoom Ayatullah Sayed Ali Aaqa Sherazi ne naql kiya hai keh yeh dua Hazrat-e-Hujjat (a) se marwi hai aur farmaya keh is dua ko waajib namaz ke baad aur digar ahem haajaat ke liye padha jaaye…", "UrduDescription": "تحفة الرضویہ میں مرحوم علامہ سید حسن فرزند مرحوم آیة اللہ سید علی آقا شیرازی سے منقول ہے کہ یہ دعا حضرت حجت سے وارد ہوئی ہے اور فرمایا ہے کہ اس دعا کو نماز یومیہ کے بعد اور اسی موقع پر اپنی حاجت روائی کے لئے پڑھی جاتی ہے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": 